{"tid":405544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家相信警察😭警方必定不偏不倚、公平公正地執法👍🏻","createTime":"2017-09-19T02:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T11:06:03.000Z","uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"775214e2ac257e164d40bdb6ebf3ad62e5c7c07b","tid":405544,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"活躍於反北區水貨客「光復上水」的社運人士、前新民主同盟社區主任梁金成，晚上到牛頭角警署報案，指立法會議員何君堯周日在添馬公園反港獨集會，與曾樹和發表的「殺無赦」論「煽動暴力及擾亂公眾秩序」。但梁指<span style=\"color: red;\">「值日官稱他們（何君堯及曾樹和）沒有實質行動」，強調「香港是言論自由的地方，他們可能只是隨意講這些話」，暫時未能立案調查。</span><br />\n<br />\n梁金成在facebook批評警方做法「搬龍門」，有網民就在帖下留言，指早前政治團體「調理農務蘭花系」成員<span style=\"color: red;\">馬健賢留言指屈穎妍「應當滅門」，卻被警以不誠實使用電腦拘捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n對於有市民舉報何君堯言論涉違法，警方發言人回覆《蘋果》查詢時僅稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人如違法，不論任何背景，警方必定果斷執法，不偏不倚、公平公正地處理。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港，勝在有特區警察！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb2e24448c631979bacb4546bc56e147b67d36f","tid":405544,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"警察好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n律政司好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0caee04a0705abde4871a48b9126dc8f17f4c7ec","tid":405544,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c356304b4117ad42d91cad0bbb474b30f102ba2","tid":405544,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0606a0c02fad5872d96f00b12ea3aba7dacab78","tid":405544,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"男殺女姦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /